data.description: Charming bungalow style home located on a huge corner lot in the Wythe section of Hampton. This home is ideal for new beginnings or a quaint living style with occasional weekend guests. Enjoy the patio, and oversized detached lighted garage w/ accessible loft with storage space or convert the garage into a small apartment. Wood chimney used 2023. H20 tank <6 yrs old, HVAC < 2yrs, new plumbing < 6yrs old.
